    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The function is straightforward, involving simple conditional logic to map input values to corresponding boroughs. Scalar functions involve basic operations and are less complex compared to table-valued functions."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
