          "type": "text",
          "text": "3. Input Parameters"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The function accepts a single input parameter, which is used to identify the borough. This parameter be a string or integer representing a code or name associated with a borough. The purpose of this parameter is to serve as the key for determining the corresponding borough."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
