          "type": "text",
          "text": "The return type of the function is a string, as it needs to return the name of a borough, such as \"Manhattan,\" \"Brooklyn,\" \"Queens,\" \"Bronx,\" or \"Staten Island.\" The structure is a single scalar value representing the borough name."
